------------------------------------------------------------
STATE STRUCTURE
------------------------------------------------------------
  this.state = {
    entryCount: 0,   // incremented by UpdateEntry()
    exitCount:  0    // incremented by UpdateExit()
  }

------------------------------------------------------------
METHODS
------------------------------------------------------------
  UpdateEntry() → setState({ entryCount: prev + 1 })
  UpdateExit()  → setState({ exitCount:  prev + 1 })
                  (guarded: exitCount cannot exceed entryCount)

